snippet.title: Cogmind - Alpha Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Alpha Access available NOW for Windows! (Linux/Mac currently Wine-only, work perfectly)
Website: http://gridsagegames.com/cogmind/ (DRM-free)
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/722730/cogmind/

If you like this trailer, you will LOVE Cogmind. What's shown here is just the beginning...

Music by Alex Yoder
http://alexyoder.net

Anyone interested in a behind-the-scenes look at how the trailer was produced, check out this production post-mortem: http://www.gridsagegames.com/blog/2015/06/making-cogminds-alpha-trailer/
